      <bioghist id="aspace_0e2c35bf9b89b52b062e4544f5efc072">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Isaac Lewis Mills (1767-1843), was a New Haven businessman and religious figure who joined the Center Church in 1806. Mills was the maternal grandfather of Edward Augustus Anketell (1840-1913), Yale College class of 1864 and Yale Law School class of 1866.</p>
         <p>Biographical informatin obtained from donor.</p>
      </bioghist>
